DoS escalation to [~andreask@atlassian.com] resulted in:

{quote}We should consider adding indexes to the oldstring column. (possibly a combined index of field and oldstring)
...
The oldstring column can contain anything from very short 1 word strings to large bits of text (for example when an issue description changed). 
...
I'd probably add a 'normal' (btree) index since that's what JIRA will do when/if we add an index to this column in JIRA. It will simply execute CREATE INDEX blah ON changeitem(oldstring);{quote}

Some parts of the quote have been removed by me.

